      • setDataReceiver

        public void setDataReceiver(ChannelDataReceiver receiver)
        For Command to install ChannelDataReceiver. When you do this, Command.setInputStream(java.io.InputStream) or AsyncCommand.setIoInputStream(org.apache.sshd.common.io.IoInputStream) will no longer be invoked. If you call this method from CommandLifecycle.start(Environment), the input stream you received in Command.setInputStream(java.io.InputStream) will not read any data.
        Parameters:
        receiver - The ChannelDataReceiver instance
